| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2461 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d76cca63-53fd-52dc-9b02-60a0da91c7d7"
